=== Закон распределения
$
P{xi = k} = 1/N \

limits(sum)_(k = 1)^N P{xi = k} = limits(sum)_(k = 1)^N 1/N = 1
$

$xi ~ R(N)$

$k = overline(1\,n)$

$P{ xi = k} = 1/N$

$
  F_xi (x) = limits(sum)_(k lt x) P{xi = k} =

  = cases(
    0\, x <= 1,
    1/N\, 1 < x <= 2,
    2/N\, 2 < x <= 3,
    dots\, dots,
    1\, x > N
  )
$

